[src:z-function-prefix/pattern-matching] We know that this is the first element because of the way lists are defined, a single element constructed onto a list.
[src:z-function-prefix/pattern-matching] The empty list would not match the pattern at all, as an empty list does not have a head (the first element that is constructed).
